<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
 * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
overflow: hidden;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

.about-image {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
}

.about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
}

.about-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(247, 238, 241, 1);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
}

.about-text-container {
    max-height: 500px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    border: 5px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);
    border-radius: 20px;
    max-width: 1000px; /* Increase the width of the border box */
    min-height: 550px;
    display: flex; /* Added */
    flex-direction: column; /* Added */
    justify-content: center; /* Added */
    align-items: center; /* Added */
    text-align: center; /* Added */
}

.about-text-container h1 {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: lighter;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
    
}

.about-text-container p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
    margin: 0; /* Added to remove default margin */
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: justify;
    padding: 0 20px; /* Optional: Add padding for left and right if needed */
}

.about-image:hover .about-overlay {
    opacity: 0.8;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/images/About US.png" alt="Workers" class="background-image">
        <div class="about-overlay">
            <div class="about-text-container">
                <h1>ABOUT US</h1>
                <p>Welcome to Kaamkriti the go-to platform for connecting local businesses with skilled workers
                    of your community. We understand the challenges faced by both businessmen looking to hire 
                    reliable labor and workers searching for job opportunities that match their skills. That's why 
                    we created a solution that bridges this gap, making it easier for everyone to find exactly what
                    they need, right when they need it.</p>
                <h1>OUR MISSION</h1>
                <p>At Kaamkriti, our mission is to empower local businesses by providing them with a reliable and 
                    efficient way to find the right talent for their needs. We are equally committed to supporting 
                    workers by offering them access to a steady stream of job opportunities, allowing them to 
                    showcase their skills and grow their careers. Our platform is designed to create a win-win 
                    situation where businesses thrive and workers succeed.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
